verbose_text: In addition, removal of 1, 2-dioleoyl-3-trimethylammonium-propane (DOTAP) from our traditional nanoparticle preparation procedure may enhance the delivery efficacy of anti-IL6R antibody to TME, which can target tumour cells as well as the TAMs and thus promote the anti-tumour effect of anti-IL6R antibody.
